43
00:04:22,100 --> 00:04:22,900
It's okay.

44
00:04:24,500 --> 00:04:25,860
Do you know

45
00:04:26,420 --> 00:04:26,980
the man who held you today?

46
00:04:27,980 --> 00:04:29,380
I was just worried about your safety.

47
00:04:29,380 --> 00:04:30,140
So...

48
00:04:31,900 --> 00:04:32,700
Zeyu,

49
00:04:33,820 --> 00:04:36,300
can you take me in tonight?

50
00:04:37,940 --> 00:04:38,620
Sure.

51
00:04:39,180 --> 00:04:40,020
Of course, I can.

52
00:04:41,100 --> 00:04:41,860
But

53
00:04:42,780 --> 00:04:45,540
are we moving too fast?

54
00:04:51,900 --> 00:04:52,580
Fine.

55
00:04:53,380 --> 00:04:54,740
I'll stay in the next room.

56
00:04:57,940 --> 00:05:00,540
