57
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:02,900
why would he be after Mr. Cao?

58
00:05:04,460 --> 00:05:05,820
What connection does he have

59
00:05:06,660 --> 00:05:08,500
with the Lin family's annihilation?

60
00:05:10,220 --> 00:05:10,820
Mengchen.

61
00:05:11,820 --> 00:05:12,660
Mengchen!

62
00:05:13,060 --> 00:05:13,980
I'm here for Mengchen.

63
00:05:14,460 --> 00:05:14,860
Mengchen!

64
00:05:14,860 --> 00:05:15,700
She's not here.

65
00:05:16,500 --> 00:05:17,100
Mengchen!

66
00:05:18,300 --> 00:05:18,940
Brother.

67
00:05:19,980 --> 00:05:20,780
What are you doing here?

68
00:05:21,220 --> 00:05:21,500
Brother,

69
00:05:21,780 --> 00:05:22,620
don't blame Mengchen.

70
00:05:22,620 --> 00:05:23,860
Don't call me brother!
I'm not your brother!

71
00:05:23,940 --> 00:05:24,340
Brother,

72
00:05:24,900 --> 00:05:26,700
we went to the masquerade ball held
by the Huaicheng Chamber of Commerce.

73
00:05:27,180 --> 00:05:28,900
Have you ever been there?

74
00:05:29,660 --> 00:05:30,820
I just thought it would be fun.

75
00:05:31,140 --> 00:05:32,540
I just wanted Mengchen to be happy.

76
00:05:32,540 --> 00:05:33,620
You don't need to worry about that.

77
00:05:34,340 --> 00:05:35,740
Brother, do you know
about masquerade balls?

78
00:05:36,300 --> 00:05:38,220
Have you ever been to any fun places

79
00:05:38,660 --> 00:05:39,820
and not taken me with you?

80
00:05:46,500 --> 00:05:46,820
Bro,

81
00:05:47,300 --> 00:05:47,980
I'm really sorry.

82
00:05:48,500 --> 00:05:49,940
It was me who took her there.

83
00:05:50,580 --> 00:05:51,380
But I truly didn't expect

84
00:05:51,380 --> 00:05:52,380
such a thing to happen.

85
00:05:54,500 --> 00:05:55,300
Go home with me.

86
00:05:58,060 --> 00:05:59,780
Brother, aren't you going
to ask what happened?

87
00:06:01,380 --> 00:06:02,180
We'll talk about it at home.

88
00:06:11,820 --> 00:06:14,630
[Nanyan Residence]

89
00:06:24,140 --> 00:06:24,620
Awake?

90
00:06:25,340 --> 00:06:25,740
Come.

91
00:06:25,940 --> 00:06:26,620
Sit down and eat.

92
00:06:32,340 --> 00:06:33,700
I've asked Mr. Sun,

93
00:06:33,700 --> 00:06:34,740
the one from the foreign firm,

94
00:06:34,900 --> 00:06:36,220
to find you

95
00:06:36,220 --> 00:06:37,020
the watch you saw in the book.

96
00:06:37,300 --> 00:06:38,060
I'll bring it back for you tomorrow.

97
00:06:39,020 --> 00:06:39,860
Thank you, brother.

98
00:06:47,420 --> 00:06:48,020
From now on,

99
00:06:48,180 --> 00:06:50,020
try not to associate with Dr. Qi anymore.

100
00:06:52,260 --> 00:06:54,980
I actually wanted to invite you
to last night's ball.

101
00:06:56,060 --> 00:06:56,540
Brother,

102
00:06:57,500 --> 00:06:58,420
where were you last night?

103
00:07:01,100 --> 00:07:02,500
I went to have dinner

104
00:07:02,500 --> 00:07:03,660
with some regular clients.

105
00:07:06,220 --> 00:07:07,100
Who were they?

106
00:07:09,220 --> 00:07:10,300
You wouldn't know them.

107
00:07:14,220 --> 00:07:15,260
Someone was killed

108
00:07:16,020 --> 00:07:16,820
at the ball last night.

109
00:07:19,540 --> 00:07:20,700
And I was carried away by someone.

110
00:07:26,460 --> 00:07:27,100
Mengchen,

111
00:07:28,980 --> 00:07:30,140
avoid such places

112
00:07:30,660 --> 00:07:31,620
from now on.

113
00:07:36,500 --> 00:07:36,940
Brother,

114
00:07:38,940 --> 00:07:39,700
would you ever lie to me?

115
00:07:41,420 --> 00:07:42,060
Or,

116
00:07:43,300 --> 00:07:44,460
would you hurt me?

117
00:07:48,860 --> 00:07:50,100
Why would I hurt you?

118
00:08:04,780 --> 00:08:05,260
Qingming,

119
00:08:08,020 --> 00:08:08,700
