120
00:08:11,780 --> 00:08:12,580
Master,

121
00:08:13,260 --> 00:08:14,620
I request to leave
the Blood Sacrifice Gang.

122
00:08:19,660 --> 00:08:20,780
It's been fifteen years...

123
00:08:36,860 --> 00:08:37,740
You brat!

124
00:08:37,900 --> 00:08:39,140
How dare you break my tobacco!

125
00:08:39,380 --> 00:08:40,260
Do you know it's worth

126
00:08:40,380 --> 00:08:41,620
more than your life?

127
00:08:43,780 --> 00:08:44,860
Fight back, huh?

128
00:08:45,180 --> 00:08:46,380
I'll beat you to death.

129
00:08:51,700 --> 00:08:52,740
It's just a bit of tobacco.

130
00:08:53,660 --> 00:08:55,020
How many lives has it cost?

131
00:08:55,180 --> 00:08:56,500
Who the hell are you?

132
00:09:13,900 --> 00:09:14,700
Just go.

133
00:09:17,620 --> 00:09:19,500
Can I follow you to fight the villains?

134
00:09:22,180 --> 00:09:23,380
Why do you want to leave?

135
00:09:24,500 --> 00:09:25,140
Over the years,

136
00:09:26,180 --> 00:09:27,620
even though we've only killed the wicked,

137
00:09:28,220 --> 00:09:29,380
