138
00:09:30,020 --> 00:09:31,180
and the inner burden weigh heavily on me.

139
00:09:31,660 --> 00:09:32,900
I'll seek a new life elsewhere.

140
00:09:38,740 --> 00:09:39,340
How about this?

141
00:09:40,220 --> 00:09:41,620
Stay for three more months.

142
00:09:42,660 --> 00:09:44,140
After all, you've been managing

143
00:09:44,300 --> 00:09:45,420
