144
00:09:45,700 --> 00:09:46,980
I need to find a suitable replacement.

145
00:09:47,900 --> 00:09:48,580
Master, rest assured.

146
00:09:49,300 --> 00:09:50,260
I will resolve

147
00:09:50,660 --> 00:09:51,580
all unfinished business

148
00:09:51,900 --> 00:09:52,820
before I leave.

